documentation.content: 3rd party career platforms have to be selected on which the job advertisement will be published.
The approved job advertisement has to be published on the homepage.
A very specific requirement to the job vacancy has to be written and forwarded to the recruitment department.
The job description edited to a job advertisement has to be checked and approved.

The job description received from the specialist department has to be completed (layout, additional information etc.) to a job advertisement in accordance to the guidelines and approved by the Hiring Manager.

triso_project_charter.triso:projectDescription: In this process, all activities are described how to advertise a job vacancy.
triso_project_charter.triso:projectScope:
Aim: Advertisement of a job vacancy conformable to law and company guidelines.
Trigger: Personnel requirements for filling job vacancies.
Result:The advertisement for the job vacancy has been reviewed and published according to the guidelines
